rComments: A prof who wants to put in no effort into teaching. This course was a waste of time. Also bad tempered.

Phillips is clearly smart, he's written some great papers, but this doesn't come through in class because he doesn't prepare lectures. He just wings it, which makes you wonder what you're paying a lot of the time. He's not good at winging it. Maybe if he prepared lectures and put in some effort he'd come across as a better prof.
